Possessing an impressive 345 lumen maximum output powering by two easily obtained AA batteries, the MT2A utilizes a CREE XP-G2 R5 LED with a 166-yard throw - not bad for such a small flashlight. Weighing in at just 2.36 ounces before battery installation, this tiny light fits firmly in the palm of your hand and can easily be carried in a pocket, purse, or backpack with a sturdy stainless-steel clip to hold it in place. With four brightness levels and two special modes easily accessed by turning the head of the light, this light is perfect for everything from common everyday tasks to taking on extended journeys, from professional inspection to personal self-defense - with a light this convenient, youre sure to constantly find new uses for your Nitecore MT2A.Nitecore MT2A Flashlight Black
